{"tid":1137330,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【痴撚線】有咩人可以做錯完野，道完歉再自己屌自己？","createTime":"2019-05-03T16:13:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T05:28:30.000Z","uid":38177,"like":11,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1812d79fc6f3532ad574ac8d4d11de410a4f2c9e","tid":1137330,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T16:13:45.000Z","msg":"杜汶澤就可以，條撚屌平時串柒柒，鳩流流，一衰左就鞠躬道歉，仲要喺自己最多人睇嗰兩個節目自己抽自己水，自己做錯事，用半集作埋首歌黎屌自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相反其他人，高官就死撐，奸商就理撚你，屌返你地轉頭。例子都唔洗舉，時事台大把<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做人做到咁撚樣，連登班五毛仲屌唔屌到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想睇杜狗自抽，自己上網搵一鳩大事回顧<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">預左收負皮，連登太多五毛同人云亦云既on99仔</span></span>"},{"pid":"952f42be1629a5d2270e92386e89eb4bc985c190","tid":1137330,"uid":60231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T17:10:56.000Z","msg":"連登囝真係唔會再出到聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36de95d19e47133a5a0bf41daf687e1ba537088e","tid":1137330,"uid":38177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"952f42be1629a5d2270e92386e89eb4bc985c190","tid":1137330,"uid":60231,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T17:10:56.000Z","msg":"連登囝真係唔會再出到聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T01:27:20.000Z","msg":"啱阿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b2c2a7e7d0132d5f2dfce77438774697d1cb429","tid":1137330,"uid":115714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-04T01:36:32.000Z","msg":"好多人都攞「係咪乜乜乜就大哂」黎做論點，但講真對比班鳩官，起碼杜汶澤柒完肯做衰仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但如果一早講會再好啲囉"},{"pi